Step 1. 
  Install JDK. //Id assume you have already.
Step 2. 
  Install Forge development environment - http://www.minecraftforge.net/wiki/Installation/Source
  Follow that link
Step 3.
  Read these pages(Read in order):
    Basic Modding - http://www.minecraftforge.net/wiki/Basic_Modding
    Crafting and Smelting - http://www.minecraftforge.net/wiki/Crafting_and_Smelting
    Basic Items - http://www.minecraftforge.net/wiki/Basic_Items
    Basic blocks - http://www.minecraftforge.net/wiki/Basic_Blocks
    Icon and Textures - http://www.minecraftforge.net/wiki/Icons_and_Textures

And now u know everything you need to know. Ez.
